May 1 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Thursday. To inform us of other job changes, email to moves@thomsonreuters.com.

MCX LTD  Multi-Commodity Exchange of India Ltd (MCX) <MCEI.NS> said on Thursday managing director and Chief Executive Manoj Vaish has resigned after just three months in office, citing health reasons. [ID:nL3N0NN19B]  BARCLAYS PLC <BARC.L> The British bank said it poached a senior banker from Commonwealth Bank of Australia (CBA) <CBA.AX> to head operations and technology. [ID:nL6N0NN1DR]  LEGG MASON INC <LM.N>